Exit codes (8):
  0  ok                         success
  1  internal                   unexpected internal error (bug or panic)
  2  usage                      invalid command syntax, flag, argument, resource ID, proxy config, or config file (JSON error kind may be usage, invalid_resource_id, invalid_proxy_config, or invalid_config)
  3  missing_credentials        credentials not configured or incomplete
  4  not_found                  resource, operation, or ID not found (JSON error kind may be not_found or unsupported_resource)
  5  live_access_failed         Zscaler API call failed (network, auth token, or quota); transient — retry is reasonable [retryable]
  6  partial_dump               dump completed but some resources failed; see errors.ndjson in the output directory
  7  drift_detected             drift check found differences between two snapshots
